Ganglia metric module for /proc/diskstats metrics

- DiskStats.py: copied from ganglia_metrics, r69279.
- GangliaMetrics.py: ditto.
- diskio.py: gmond compatibility wrapper for the files above.
- diskio.pyconf: gmond module config file.

The ganglia_metrics package may be obtained from
<http://svn.wikimedia.org/viewvc/mediawiki/trunk/ganglia_metrics/?pathrev=69279>
